query_1_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) AS transaction_count, SUM(amount) AS total_amount, DATE(timestamp) AS transaction_date FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U007' AND timestamp >= DATE('2025-06-01') AND timestamp < DATE('2025-07-01') GROUP BY DATE(timestamp) ORDER BY transaction_date;
query_2_sql: SELECT t.transaction_id, t.amount, t.timestamp, t.location, t.device_id, t.ip_address FROM transactions t JOIN alerts a ON t.transaction_id = a.transaction_id WHERE t.user_id = 'U007' AND a.alert_type = 'Velocity' AND t.timestamp >= DATE('2025-06-01') AND t.timestamp < DATE('2025-07-01') ORDER BY t.timestamp DESC;
query_3_sql: SELECT la.timestamp, la.ip_address, la.device_id, la.status FROM login_attempts la WHERE la.user_id = 'U007' AND la.timestamp >= DATE('2025-06-01') AND la.timestamp < DATE('2025-07-01') ORDER BY la.timestamp DESC;
query_4_sql: SELECT t.transaction_id, t.amount, t.timestamp, t.location, t.device_id, t.ip_address FROM transactions t WHERE t.user_id = 'U007' AND t.location != (SELECT registered_location FROM users WHERE user_id = 'U007') AND t.timestamp >= DATE('2025-06-01') AND t.timestamp < DATE('2025-07-01') ORDER BY t.timestamp DESC;
query_5_sql: SELECT d.device_id, d.device_type, d.os, d.last_seen_ip FROM devices d JOIN user_devices ud ON d.device_id = ud.device_id WHERE ud.user_id = 'U007' AND d.last_seen_ip != (SELECT ip_address FROM transactions WHERE transaction_id = '4d183eba-3cd5-4d7f-89c1-444444444444') ORDER BY d.last_seen_ip;
query_6_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) as txn_count, SUM(amount) as total_amount FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U007' AND timestamp > datetime('now', '-1 hour')
query_7_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT payee_id) as unique_payees FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U007' AND timestamp > datetime('now', '-1 hour')
query_9_sql: SELECT * FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U007' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
query_10_sql: SELECT * FROM login_attempts WHERE user_id = 'U007' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
query_12_sql: SELECT d.* FROM devices d JOIN user_devices ud ON d.device_id = ud.device_id WHERE ud.user_id = 'U007';
